  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Describe image formation by spherical mirrors.</item>
<item>Use ray diagrams and the mirror equation to calculate the properties of an image in a spherical mirror.</item>
</list></md:abstract>
